t" title="Public access to documents">Public access to documents<i class="fa fa-caret-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></li><li><a href="/en/about-ecdc/who-we-are/key-documents/eueea-routine-surveillance-open-data-policy" title="EU/EEA routine surveillance open data policy">EU/EEA routine surveillance open data policy<i class="fa fa-caret-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></li></ul></div></div></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4"><div class="child-page__item"><h3 class="child-page__title h4"><a href="/en/about-us/ecdcs-governance" title="Read more about: Governance">Governance<i class="fa fa-caret-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h3><div class="child-page__description"><ul><li><a href="/en/about-ecdc/who-we-are/governance/management-board" title="Management Board">Management Board<i class="fa fa-caret-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></li><li><a href="/en/about-ecdc/who-we-are/governance/advisory-forum" title="Advisory Forum">Advisory Forum<i class="fa fa-caret-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></li><li><a href="/en/about-ecdc/who-we-are/governance/competent-bodies" title="Competent Bodies">Competent Bodies<i class="fa fa-caret-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></li><li><a href="/en/about-ecdc/who-we-are/governance/audit-committee" title="Audit Committee">Audit Committee<i class="fa fa-caret-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></li></ul></div></div></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4"><div class="child-page__item"><h3 class="child-page__title h4"><a href="/en/about-us/who-we-are/director-ecdc" title="Read more about: Director of ECDC">Director of ECDC<i class="fa fa-caret-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h3><div class="child-page__description"><ul><li><a href="/en/about-us/who-we-are/organisational-structure/director-ecdc/former-directors" title="Former Directors">Former Directors<i class="fa fa-caret-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div>
